<h1>Orderly Book</h1>

<div class="docbody">
<div class="opener">
<table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">[2 October 1758]</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<p style="text-indent: 0;">Camp at Reas Town Monday Octr 2d 1758</p>
<p style="text-indent: 0;">G. O.</p>
<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0;">Parole Louisan</p>
<p>Colo. for to Morrow Colo. Washington.<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0043-fn-0001" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0043-fn-0001-ptr">1</a></p>
<p>Field Officer for to Morrow Lt Colo. Work.</p>
<p>Adjt for to morrow 3d Battallion.</p>
